message.body: ...Baby...i missed my bus
Did you just wake up?
Yes
I'm in lab. You can see if they'll still let you on
Up to you.
What did you do, baby?
Ive gotta stay here, baby. Im so so sorry. I feel terrible. Im gonna stay and do my assignments :-(
I keep hoping that you were punking me and that you'll come knock on my door -_- I'm so sad...
Oh baby i would never do that. Im so mad at myself. Im sorry Jenny
I'm a little mad at you too! But I'll get over it. I still love you.
I...i hope so! But really, im sorry. This is serious motivation to become a person again and stop working nights.
:/ don't worry.
I dont like it, baby. Not at all
I don't like it either.
I'm over it now! Hiiii!
Doing good. How are you? Work?
Still at Yakatori Boy? Hows the partay? Im good. HW and applications. Definitely not at work.
No we're at tango right now. Yay!!!! Good. I'd be mad if you were at work
Not the dance. The bar :)
Hahah i figured it was a bar. Didnt think that crew would be tango-ing. Hope everyone is having fun! And, if youre not sleepy, i'll be up til...forever ha
Haha. Okie! Still awake and here! But I'll text you to see if you're awake later.
No worries, my love. You have fun!
Awake?
But of course
Geronimo. Listen to it if you want a good pick me up song.
It's good. It's by Shepard :) I love you and goodnight for real now.
Haha thanks my love :) I'll listen. Sleep well!!
You're welcome :D I'm not quite sure how a man can go that high, but I like the chorus.
Ahaha imma listen after i finish this essay :-p Listening might derail ma focus
Good idea. I listened to it before trying to go to bed...and now I can't go to bed cause I want to keep listening to it.
Haha i was wondering how you hadnt fallen asleep yet :)
This friggin song.
Haha at least you like it and theres nothing awful swirling around in your head
Nope. I'm dancing in my bed.
Haha dammit come on i wanna be there with you
Haha come on baby. Dance with me!!!
Hahah you know i would!
I know!
